=head1 NAME

SimpleLinks - sample application of collection of links (with Ark and Data::Model)


=head1 INSTALLATION

To install this application,

first, to make Makefile, build this application and run tests
by the following command:

    cpan -t .

next, to deploy this application
by the following command:

    cpan -i .


=head1 DEPENDENCIES

See C<Makefile.PL>.


=head1 DESCRIPTION

This is Perl sample application,
with Ark framework and Data::Model object/data mapper.

See further document of this application by the following commands:

    perldoc SimpleLinks


